 A very tasty recipe, easy to follow. 

00:00:42.920 --> 00:00:47.320
 The ingredients are: sheep's milk pecorino cheese, Parmesan, best-quality bacon / pork cheek, 

00:00:47.320 --> 00:00:54.440
 some more bacon / pork cheek, later I'll tell you why, garlic, an egg, egg yolks, some salt, pasta, oil and pepper. 

